This paper deals with image processing using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper specifically focuses on joint demosaicking and denoising, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The use of neural networks for this task also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves image restoration, which is a topic in graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper deals with the processing of raw images, which is a topic in image processing (cs.IR).
